WEBVTT

00:02:28.714 --> 00:02:32.830
na Juni Mosi Elfu mwaka wa Mbili na Tisa
ilikuwa siku tuliyopanga kufika uwanjani


00:02:32.830 --> 00:02:34.889
na kujaribu kupata sikio la rais.


00:02:34.889 --> 00:02:36.329
Ilikuwa siku kuu,


00:02:36.329 --> 00:02:37.978
sherehe yenyewe ilitangazwa kote nchini,


00:02:37.978 --> 00:02:41.386
na nilifika uwanjani.


00:02:41.386 --> 00:02:44.380
Marafiki zangu hawakutokea.


00:02:44.380 --> 00:02:47.753
Nilijipata peke yangu,


00:02:47.753 --> 00:02:50.280
na sikujua la kufanya.


00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:51.695
Niliogopa,


00:02:51.695 --> 00:02:53.865
lakini nilifahamu vyema kuwa siku hiyo,


00:02:53.865 --> 00:02:55.086
Nilihitaji kufanya uamuzi.


00:02:55.086 --> 00:02:57.509
Ningeweza kuishi kama mwoga,
kama watu wengine,


00:02:57.509 --> 00:02:59.107
au ningechukua msimamo thabiti?


00:02:59.107 --> 00:03:01.313
Na rais aliposimama kuhutubu,
